{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}
{% block body %}
    <div class="container">

        <h1 class="d-flex justify-content-center">Welcome to the DEV TEST</h1>
        <p class="d-flex justify-content-center">Thank you for taking part on our test</p>

        <h3>Step 1: <small>Creating Routes and Displaying elements</small></h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Create a page called Locations with the url "/location".</li>
            <li>This page will have a list of all elements from <b>"Location"</b> entity.</li>
            <li>Each element should be a link to the location page that will be created on step 2.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Step 2: <small>Database Query and Advanced Routes</small></h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Create a page for each <b>"Location"</b> using the slug as reference for the url eg. "/location/london"
            </li>
            <li>Display on this page the elements from the entity <b>"Property"</b> that are within 1 mile range from
                the
                <b>"Location"</b> using the Latitude and Longitude as the measure method.
            </li>
            <li>Each element should be a link to the "Property" page that will be created on step 3.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Step 3: <small>Forms</small></h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Create a page for each <b>"Property"</b> using the ID as reference for the url eg. "/property/2"</li>
            <li>This page will show all details from the Property object plus the <b>"Enquiry"</b> objects that are
                related
                to this property
            </li>
            <li>This page will have a <b>Enquire</b> form that once submitted will save to the database the enquire
                (message
                and email).
            </li>
            <li>This form must have email validation and only accept valid emails.</li>
        </ul>
        <hr>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-6">
                <h3>Notes:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Please demonstrate familiarity with the symfony ecosystem.</li>
                    <li>Completing and implementing the services "FindLocation" and "FindProperty" is desired.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="col-6">
                <h3>Entities:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Location</li>
                    <li>Enquire</li>
                    <li>Property</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
{% endblock %}